    <tags>korean ime hangul hotkey shift-space keyboard lightweight portable</tags>
    <summary>Ultra-lightweight Shift+Space Korean/English IME toggle for Windows (4.5KB)</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
**nShiftSpace** (Nexa ShiftSpace) is an ultra-lightweight Windows tray utility
that toggles the Korean/English IME with **Shift+Space** — the classic Korean
keyboard layout behavior.

- Single 4.5KB executable, no C runtime, pure Win32 API
- Zero CPU while idle (uses `RegisterHotKey`, no keyboard hook)
- Tray icon with exit menu, single-instance guard
- Free and open source (MIT)

To run at login, put a shortcut into `shell:startup`.
]]></description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/SosomLab/nexa-shortcut/releases</releaseNotes>
